<h1>About us</h1>
<p>At <strong>FeeCast</strong>, we are improving the way people make their decisions about healthcare by providing price transparency to health services, from doctor visits to surgeries.</p>

<p><strong>For patients</strong> – using our online trusted source, we provide you with multiple health professionals nearby and their respective prices for your needs. You can compare and request an appointment with a health professional based on prices, ratings and reviews, accreditations, distance, and more. And best of all, FeeCast membership is free.</p>

<p><strong>For health service professionals</strong> – we help providers and healthcare facilities, such as surgery centers and clinics, drive patients to you. With FeeCast, we connect you with qualified patients with real healthcare needs. Increase your patient flow and list your practice or facility today.</p>